data.description: GREAT PROPERTY FOR HANDY HOMEBUYER OR INVESTOR in WHISPERWOOD.      Many important updates already done.      This 2 bedroom, 2 & 1/2 bath townhouse has a 3 year old roof,  new copper water pipes (polybutylene pipes replaced), all 3 baths redone with tile floors, new tub showers and sinks,  plus recent carpets and the main line to the sewer was also replaced.    Wood burning fireplace in the Living Room with sliding door to brick patio.   Kitchen has a wide pass through to Dining & Living area so the chef knows what's going on.  Half bath off entry hall on main.      Upstairs Primary suite offers two closets and a private sink/vanity separate from upstairs full bath.    Second bedroom (or office) also upstairs.         Full basement includes a finished Recreation Room with closet, new tub/shower bath with tile floor and a separate laundry/utilities room.          One Reserved Parking Spot with plenty of unreserved parking surrounding and throughout the neighborhood.          This home is perhaps a half mile to recreational Lake Thoreau and Lake Audubon, with South Lakes shopping center across the causeway between the lakes (by community paved trail, car or bike) with restaurants, banking, Safeway and shopping.         Reston amenities including Community Trails, Pools, Tennis Courts, Nature Center, Library, Playgrounds and more.          Easy access to Reston Town Center, Dulles Toll Road, Fairfax County Parkway, Metro Silver Line plus Bus service.      Community trail goes directly to High School and Middle School through a small woods from near the house.  Elementary School and a Montessori School both very close.
